## 5.4 API 3：阅读热力图

### 接口

```text id="bq9pnv"
GET /api/profile/reading-heatmap?days=30&dimension=category
```

### 作用

生成分类或话题在日期维度上的活跃度矩阵。

### 第一版推荐维度

```text id="ty1h0z"
x 轴：日期
y 轴：新闻分类
value：阅读次数
```

后续可以扩展：

```text id="m6vzp8"
x 轴：小时
y 轴：星期
value：阅读次数
```

### 返回结构

```json id="gqnny6"
{
  "code": 200,
  "message": "success",
  "data": {
    "x_axis": ["2026-06-20", "2026-06-21", "2026-06-22"],
    "y_axis": ["科技", "财经", "社会", "体育"],
    "cells": [
      {
        "x": "2026-06-20",
        "y": "科技",
        "value": 3,
        "news_count": 3
      },
      {
        "x": "2026-06-21",
        "y": "财经",
        "value": 2,
        "news_count": 2
      }
    ],
    "summary": {
      "max_value": 5,
      "most_active_category": "科技",
      "most_active_date": "2026-06-24"
    }
  }
}
```

### 计算规则

```text id="zgfu1e"
按 日期 + 分类 聚合 COUNT(*)
```

SQL 思路：

```sql id="8tg00x"
SELECT
  DATE(bh.browse_time) AS read_date,
  nc.name AS category_name,
  COUNT(*) AS read_count
FROM browse_history bh
JOIN news n ON n.id = bh.news_id
LEFT JOIN news_category nc ON nc.id = n.category_id
WHERE bh.user_id = %s
  AND bh.browse_time >= DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL %s DAY)
GROUP BY DATE(bh.browse_time), nc.name
ORDER BY read_date ASC;
```

